channel.title: Mining won't work and wood cutting is to slow. PLEASE HELP
channel.description: Okay so my runite rocks when ever I click on them it says "objectid: 14859 ObjectX:2839 object 3439" Any way to fix this? because i really need it fixed... I also have a problem with wood cutting being super slow. it takes almost a full minute with 99 wc to get 1 magic log. PLEASE HELP

item.dc:creator: @3lv3n_snip3r 3lv3n snip3r
item.description:
@3lv3n_snip3r wrote:

What it is saying is obviously the object id and the positioning of the object… You have to add it into your Mining and ActionHandler classes if you use cases for your mining. For the woodcutting, go try cutting a magic log in RuneScape with 99 woodcutting. It isn’t nearly a minute, but it’s over 30 seconds for 1 log. Anyways, you’ll have to search through your Woodcutting class.
